OL,3,CFootballing great John Toshack
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with dementia
OL,6,FLiverpool FC and Wales great John
OL,7,FToshack has been diagnosed with
OL,8,Fdementia, his son Cameron has said.
OL,10,FToshack scored more than 100 goals and
OL,11,Fwon nine trophies with the Reds
OL,12,Fbetween 1970 and 1978.
OL,14,FHe earned 40 caps for Wales before
OL,15,Fturning to management, including roles
OL,16,Fwith Real Sociedad, Real Madrid and
OL,17,Fhis national team.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
