PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774469469
OL,3,CFootballing great John Toshack
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with dementia
OL,6,FThe 77-year-old's son Cameron, who
OL,7,Fworks as football coach in Thailand
OL,8,Fand was formerly assistant manager at
OL,9,FLeeds, told the Daily Mail that
OL,10,FToshack goes through good and bad days
OL,11,Fas he battles dementia.
OL,13,FHe said: "It's a terrible disease.
OL,14,FIt's the short-term memory where we're
OL,15,Fseeing it ` I speak to him most days
OL,16,Fand if we chat in the afternoon, he
OL,17,Fmight not remember that we also spoke
OL,18,Fin the morning.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774469469
OL,3,CFootballing great John Toshack
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with dementia
OL,6,F"But if I ask him about the Liverpool
OL,7,Fdays, or Sociedad or Madrid, the
OL,8,Fdetail is amazing.
OL,10,F"The other day he was telling me about
OL,11,Fa Real Madrid game against Arrigo
OL,12,FSacchi's AC Milan and exactly how he
OL,13,Ftweaked his midfield to deal with
OL,14,FMarco van Basten.
OL,16,F"The game could have been yesterday,
OL,17,Fhis memory was so clear.
OL,19,F"I'll talk to him about what we're
OL,20,Fdoing in Thailand and he still gives
OL,21,Fgreat advice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
