FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774469469
OL,3,CFootballing great John Toshack
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with dementia
OL,6,F"As a manager, he could always see two
OL,7,For three moves ahead, and it was
OL,8,Falways in the genes for me, really."
OL,10,FToshack began his career at hometown
OL,11,Fclub Cardiff before signing for Bill
OL,12,FShankly's Liverpool, where he was part
OL,13,Fof teams that won three league titles,
OL,14,Ftwo UEFA Cups, an FA Cup and a
OL,15,FEuropean Cup.
OL,17,FIn his first job in management he took
OL,18,FSwansea from the old fourth division
OL,19,Fto the top tier, and then took charge
OL,20,Fat Sporting Lisbon in Portugal before
OL,21,Fmoving to Spain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]
