FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774469469
OL,3,CFootballing great John Toshack
OL,4,Cdiagnosed with dementia
OL,6,FHe won the Copa del Rey during one of
OL,7,Fthree spells at Real Sociedad and
OL,8,Ftwice managed Real Madrid, winning
OL,9,FLaLiga in 1990 with a record 107 goals
OL,10,Fscored.
OL,12,FToshack also coached in France,
OL,13,FTurkey, Morocco, Azerbaijan and
OL,14,FMacedonia and had two stints as Wales
OL,15,Fboss.
OL,17,FIn his second spell, between 2004 and
OL,18,F2010, Toshack gave debuts to Aaron
OL,19,FRamsey, Gareth Bale and others who
OL,20,Fbecame mainstays of the side that
OL,21,Freached the semi-finals of Euro 2016.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
